Hack Asynchronous I/O Helpers
asio


 &reftitle.intro;


  The ASIO helpers provide convenient functions to use when writing async code.



     Some of the asio helpers are currently, in our opinion, still a bit unstable. We have moved these to its own HHVM repo where they can be installed as a composer package. In this documentation, helper functions will be noted and pointed to that repo.





   Here is an overview of the currently built-in, supported API. Use the appropraite method whether you want a vector or map of Awaitables:




         v - Vector





         m - Map






